      <title>Currys 股价因盈利预期和股息回升而上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/currys-restores-dividend-with-cost-controls-improving-outlook</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Currys Plc 恢复派息后股价飙升，该公司表示，由于严格控制成本，预计今年利润将更高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/currys-restores-dividend-with-cost-controls-improving-outlook</guid>
