    <item>
      <title>Synthesia，一家制作神奇人工智能头像的初创公司，估值达 21 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/video-ai-startup-synthesia-raises-180-million-at-2-1-billion-valuation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Synthesia 是一家人工智能初创公司，可帮助企业制作逼真的视频头像，该公司在一轮融资中筹集了 1.8 亿美元，成为英国最大的人工智能公司之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/video-ai-startup-synthesia-raises-180-million-at-2-1-billion-valuation</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 06:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Mozilla 因拒绝聘用苹果活动人士而达成和解</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/mozilla-settles-case-over-its-refusal-to-hire-apple-activist</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Mozilla 公司已同意就其因一名前苹果公司软件工程师之前的劳工激进主义行为而拒绝聘用她的指控达成和解。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/mozilla-settles-case-over-its-refusal-to-hire-apple-activist</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 05:24:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国将敦促台积电和三星限制向中国供应芯片</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/us-to-push-tsmc-and-samsung-to-tighten-flow-of-chips-to-china</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国计划出台更多法规，旨在阻止台湾半导体制造公司和其他生产商生产的先进芯片流向中国，这是拜登政府执政最后几天推出的一系列措施之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/us-to-push-tsmc-and-samsung-to-tighten-flow-of-chips-to-china</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 05:01:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国的凯尔·斯塔默需要抑制他的人工智能热情</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/opinion/articles/2025-01-15/starmer-s-ai-vision-for-the-uk-could-use-a-reality-check</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加倍加强国家在人工智能方面的强有力监管领导作用，将比追求模糊和不确定的产业政策更为明智。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/opinion/articles/2025-01-15/starmer-s-ai-vision-for-the-uk-could-use-a-reality-check</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 05:00:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>洛杉矶大火一周后狂风大作，且无降雨迹象</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/after-week-of-flames-la-faces-high-winds-and-no-sign-of-rain</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南加州居民已经历了一周的山林大火、疏散、停电和学校关闭，他们又将面临又一个严重火灾危险的夜晚，因为回归的圣安娜风有可能在整个地区煽动火势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/after-week-of-flames-la-faces-high-winds-and-no-sign-of-rain</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 Jan 2025 22:50:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
